{
  "text": "Because a similar scoring system was recently used to demonstrate significantly increased P-gp staining of endothelial cells following kainate-induced seizures (Seegers et al. 2002a,b) , analysis of endothelial staining was not performed again in the present experiments. Furthermore, we recently used computer-assisted image analysis of endothelial P-gp staining based on optical density measurements, which demonstrated a significant increase of endothelial P-gp expression after kainate treatment [CITATION_1] ). Detection, however, was possible in acetone-fixed sections only and was not repeated in the present experiments.",
